      "value": "Conditional processing"
    },
    {
      "fieldId": "1a000002-0000-4000-a000-000000000002",
      "value": "\nAudience, platform, and output filtering may eventually allow one source Container to produce different projections for different readers. This is deferred because SectionSource queries already cover common projection differences, while a general condition evaluation model would add substantial complexity."
    }
